  'undergoing a spiritual transformation. Pendants such as this one were hung around the neck, '
  'often attached to pectoral discs or sewn onto elaborate textiles signifying rank. In the Gran '
  'Coclé area of Panama numerous artifacts have been found that relate to the lives of the people '
