  'bill features the portrait of President Lincoln’s Secretary of the Treasury, Salmon P. Chase. A '
  'true collector’s item, almost all $10,000 notes have been removed from circulation and '
  'destroyed by the Federal Reserve, though some are still held in museum collections such as the '
  'Museum of American Finance in New York. This particular bill was once a part of the famed '
