  'traditional still life category. The multicolored blossoms rest upon a light blue surface, '
  'while the floral forms provide a visually stimulating play on light and movement, heightened by '
  'Valtat’s quick and measured strokes of paint. Anémones et Jonquilles au pichet vert showcases '
