  'diminutive figure bounces across the high wire as the three musicians appear to accompany him '
  'with their song. The musical movement is hidden within the wooden base; once activated, it '
  'plays simultaneously with the movements of the figures above. The scene itself unfolds '
  'underneath glass dome, which not only provides protection, but also reinforces the sense that '
  'the scene is a small world unto itself. Considered by many to be the precursor to the computer, '
