  "refinement and elegance, the creamer's Baroque-style body is perfectly balanced by its scrolled "
  'handle and accented with delicate beading and gadrooning. Commissioned by one of the most '
  'renowned families in American history, the Alden family, this creamer has incredible '
  "provenance. John Alden was one of the few single men aboard the Mayflower's maiden voyage to "
