  'and labor-intensive, the frames that surrounded these treasured items, were important in both '
  'function and design. This remarkable mirror is distinguished not only by its original, large '
  'silvered glass, but also by its exceptional cushioned frame, adorned in elaborate marquetry of '
  'inlaid walnut. An undeniably exquisite example of 17th century English quality construction and '
