  'creatures are inspired by the tales of the mythical early settlers of Ireland by the same name. '
  'Introduced by Wedgwood artist Daisy Makeig-Jones in 1915, Fairyland Lustre marked a true '
  "departure from the factory's history of classic design and subdued colors. Makeig-Jones' work "
