  'in a striking replica of a Neoclassical temple. Crafted of luxurious bumblebee satinwood, two '
  'Doric columns support the tapered roof as meticulous hand-carving adorns the front pediment, '
  'frieze, and panels. This decoration is beautifully echoed on the pierced side panels and '
  'friezes for a fluid consistency. A pierced and engraved center plate dominates the dial, which '
  "features Arabic numerals and the maker's cartouche. The mechanism itself is spring-wound and "
