  'finest royal provenance, originating from the private collection of Queen Victoria. They would '
  "have graced her grand banquets, serving not only the Queen herself but also the world's elite. "
  'Each tazza-inspired stand is marked with her monogram, "VR" for Victoria Regina, and hallmarked '
