  'tranquility. Born the son of famed sporting and equestrian painter John Frederick Herring, Sr., '
  'Herring the younger was raised surrounded by fine painting, and developed a love of painting '
  'under his father’s influence, as did his younger brothers Charles and Benjamin. In fact, he '
